53
00:03:19,020 --> 00:03:20,220
I can't remember anything.

54
00:03:25,060 --> 00:03:25,940
Get dressed.

55
00:03:26,580 --> 00:03:27,460
I'll drive you home.

56
00:03:29,100 --> 00:03:29,420
Hey.

57
00:03:35,020 --> 00:03:35,620
I...

58
00:03:36,820 --> 00:03:39,340
