107
00:07:18,340 --> 00:07:19,780
Mu, I really admire you.

108
00:07:25,180 --> 00:07:26,220
Your memory is back?

109
00:07:28,940 --> 00:07:29,620
Sorry

110
00:07:29,980 --> 00:07:30,860
